OL,3,CPrincess Royal attends dawn Anzac Day
OL,4,Cservice at Hyde Park
OL,6,FThe Princess Royal attended a dawn
OL,7,Fservice at Wellington Arch, Hyde Park
OL,8,FCorner to mark Anzac Day.
OL,10,FOrganised by the New Zealand and
OL,11,FAustralian High Commissions, Anne
OL,12,Farrived for the service shortly before
OL,13,Fit started at 5am.
OL,15,FAnzac Day commemorates the 1915
OL,16,FGallipoli landing of Australian and
OL,17,FNew Zealand troops in the First World
OL,18,FWar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
