OL,3,CPrincess Royal attends dawn Anzac Day
OL,4,Cservice at Hyde Park
OL,6,FServices were held across New Zealand,
OL,7,FAustralia and Gallipoli on Saturday
OL,8,Fmorning.
OL,10,FThe occasion was also marked in
OL,11,FVillers-Bretonneux, a village in the
OL,12,FSomme region of France, which
OL,13,FAustralian units helped defend during
OL,14,Fthe First World War.
