OL,3,CPrincess Royal attends dawn Anzac Day
OL,4,Cservice at Hyde Park
OL,6,FA post on the Royal Family X account
OL,7,Fon Saturday morning read: "Today is
OL,8,F_ANZACDay ` which honours the members
OL,9,Fof the Australian and New Zealand Army
OL,10,FCorps (ANZAC) who served and died in
OL,11,Fall wars, conflicts and peacekeeping
OL,12,Foperations."
